# Waby — Design System

Brand: **Waby**. Logo is a butterfly (navy wings + a blue dot). Friendly, rounded, calm.
`lib/core/theme.dart` is the source of truth — use `AppColors` constants, never raw hex in widgets.

## Colours (exact)
- Primary navy `#0F2D54` — main buttons, headings.
- Logo wings / darkest text `#0D1117`.
- Wave-header gradient `#4696B7` → `#4C9DBC`.
- Accent blue `#3B74BC` — links, info pills.
- Value blue `#5187C6` — big stat numbers.
- Logo dot / bright accent `#2AAEE0`.
- Soft light blue `#8ECEE1` — bottom nav, soft accents.
- Field background `#F7F3F3`.
- Safe child card `#E0E8F2`; warning child card `#FBE6E5`; plain cards `#FFFFFF`.
- Status: SAFE green `#56B337`; WARNING / critical red `#C2291D`.

## Typography
Poppins (via `google_fonts`). Big bold headings, bold coloured values, grey secondary text.

## Recurring components
- **Wave header** — gradient banner with a white wavy bottom edge + page title.
- **Status pill** — rounded badge, green SAFE / red WARNING.
- **Info pill** — blue rounded chip with icon + label (Latched, Near, 88%).
- **Child card** — avatar + name + DOB/weight + status badge + row of info pills; background tinted by status (blue safe / pink warning).
- **Metric card** — white rounded card with icon, "LIVE" chip, label, big blue value, subtitle (2×2 grid on detail page).
- **Primary button** — full-width navy, ~16px radius, bold white text, often a right arrow.
- **Bottom nav** — rounded light-blue bar, 3 tabs (Home / Family / Setting).
- **Alert screen** — full-screen colour gradient (red for temp/danger), big icon, bold title, subtitle, navy Acknowledge button.

## Icons
Mostly Material Icons (`Icons.home`, `Icons.bluetooth`, `Icons.link`, `Icons.thermostat`, battery, gps). Use the exported PNG assets for the baby, gender, and family glyphs.
